title: Player Attack S03E14 720p HDTV h264-Berg
description:
This week, we're in Poland! We headed to Europe for the World of Tanks 2015 Grand Final, and it was a pretty awesome experience. We've got all the highlights for you in one neat little package - including interviews with professional gamers from around the world, a chat with the Wargaming team including CEO Victor Kislyi, and some of the world's best Tanks gameplay, direct from the show floor. (We also get up close and personal with a Sherman tank, which is impressive in its own right!)

Plus, of course, we have all the latest gaming news - this is Player Attack!
